videos.description: Zion Williamson pokes the ball away from Donovan Mitchell, then Lonzo Ball grabs the rock and dunks it down in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion's steal leads to Lonzo's dunk) 2021/03/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion's steal leads to Lonzo's dunk

videos.description: Jordan Clarkson tosses one up to Donovan Mitchell, who slams it down with authority.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell gets up for an alley-oop jam) 2021/03/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell gets up for an alley-oop jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson kicks it out to JJ Redick, who knocks down a 3-pointer.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Zion makes great assist while falling) 2021/03/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion makes great assist while falling

videos.description: Donovan Mitchell rears back to dunk it down, but it clanks off the back rim, leading to a Josh Hart layup the other way.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Mitchell's blown dunk sparks Hart's layup the other way) 2021/03/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Mitchell's blown dunk sparks Hart's layup the other way

videos.description: Mike Conley forces up a bad 3-pointer to tie the game, then the Pelicans get out in transition with a Josh Hart jam.

videos.headline: Pelicans lock up Jazz on tying attempt, then Hart adds cherry on top

videos.description: Zion Williamson scores 15 of his 26 points in the third quarter as New Orleans beats Utah 129-124.
